      "content": "Hey, I'm looking over the annual reports for the South Sudan fund before I decide on the renewal for next year. To be honest, I've been seeing a lot of news about NGOs having huge overhead costs lately. Can you give me a breakdown of how much of my last donation actually reached the field vs how much is just being spent on staff and marketing?",
